member.param:
Indicates whether to wrap the datetime value in a pair of slashes.
If true, the datetime value will be in this format:'/Date(1xxxxxxxxxxxx+yyyy)/';
otherwise, no prefix and surfix:'Date(1xxxxxxxxxxxx+yyyy)'.
